      "title": "Set Camp",
      "summary": "Create a campsite.",
      "body": "Usage: Establish a modest campsite in your current room. Requirements: you must know Set Camp, be standing, be out of combat, and the room must allow camping. Typical purpose: creates a campsite for resting and follow-up survival abilities. Related abilities: Build Campfire.",
